# Arrays Interview Preparation Roadmap

This repository contains frequently asked Array interview questions from top product-based companies like Juspay, Atlassian, Salesforce, Microsoft, Amazon, and others.

The problems are categorized into Easy, Medium, and Hard levels for structured preparation.

---

# Easy Level

1. Find Largest Element
2. Find Second Largest Element
3. Check if Array is Sorted
4. Remove Duplicates from Sorted Array
5. Move Zeroes to End
6. Reverse an Array
7. Left Rotate Array by 1 Place
8. Left Rotate Array by K Places
9. Find Missing Number (1 to N)
10. Find Single Number (all others appear twice)
11. Union of Two Sorted Arrays
12. Intersection of Two Sorted Arrays
13. Count Frequency of Elements
14. Find Leaders in Array
15. Linear Search
16. Maximum Consecutive Ones
17. Find Majority Element (> n/2 times)

---

